    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. It currently requires significant mechanical attention to be roadworthy, and the engine exhibits a noticeable knock. The exterior has substantial rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the paint is heavily oxidized. Inside, the upholstery is torn in several places and the electronics are inconsistent. Please expect to invest time and resources into repairs.",
