    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! It shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, but it still runs well and offers a dependable way to get from A to B. It's a great choice for anyone looking for a solid, functional car at an accessible price point!",
